  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Preoperative anxiety can be detected via structured and standardised screening by the State -
      Trait Anxiety Inventory (STAI) and Self rating Depression Scale (SDS) questionnaire. The
      investigators evaluate the relation of perioperative anxiety and heart rate variability, also
      the impact of general anesthesia on the change of heart rate variability.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
